app_description: ParlaAI is a journaling app that utilizes the latest technology from OpenAI. It allows users to create daily journal entries and receive personalized tips and recommendations based on their daily events. Think of it as a coach that helps you navigate daily life with useful tools and advice. Additionally Parla provides users with a sentiment score and mental health score for the week enabling them to set goals and track progress towards their desired mental health.
